These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, australian, mexican, polish
1. the australian is in an odd position##4
2. the polish is between the pakistani and the australian##2
3. the polish is on the right of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | pakistani | polish | australian | mexican |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, onion, corn, grapefruit
1. the person eating peach is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the person eating onion is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | onion | peach | grapefruit | corn |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, epic, superhero, comedy
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
2. the person watching spy movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching superhero movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching epic movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | comedy | superhero | epic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, cricket, skiing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
2. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person who's sport is skiing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | cricket | volleyball | tennis | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, climbing, baseball, parkour
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | parkour | volleyball | baseball | climbing |

