.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, potato, zucchini, kale
1. the person eating potato is the person eating potato##1
2. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
3. the person eating zucchini is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating cherry is in an even position##4
5. the person eating kale is on the left of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | zucchini | kale | potato | cherry |

