1. the accountant is in an odd position##4
2. the fisherman is on the left of the accountant##1
3. the accountant is on the left or right of the electrician##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Job   | teacher | fisherman | accountant | electrician |

 